CHANGES
=======

0.2
---

* version 0.2.0
* fix README
* README.md
* disable wheel downloads - c extensions in wheel (e.g. home built lxml!) fail at run-time on slightly different linux versions
* refactor + fix tests + refine command outputs
* delegate http repo uploads to twine (license & responsibility cleanup)
* status command: show python packaging configuration status
* new README
* 
* use command: makes backup of existing config before writing ~/.pip/pip.conf
* refactor - move functionality to its proper place
* tox.ini: default to py27 environment, 3.* does NOT work
* dummy test for main, to make code uncovered with tests visible
* README - changelog
* add known repos on first run + new command import_pypirc
* save readline history between sessions
* improve output on exception
* reworked shell intro - shorter and includes version
* preparing for version 0.1.4

0.1.3
-----

* prepare for release 0.1.3
* refine message on upload error
* upload continues with next package even when there are http error responses

0.1.2
-----

* README: early release notice
* setup.cfg: fix keywords & classifiers

